title: Greengages Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has gluten-free, vegetarian and vegan food. Uses local products. Menu includes vegetable lentil stew with rice, jacket potato with the lentil stew as a filling, and a black bean burger. Has soy milk for hot drinks. Sells jams and packets of tea.
